Key Market Drivers
1. Rising Demand in Consumer Electronics
The PC Diffuser Film Market is being propelled by a surge in demand for high‑performance displays in smartphones, tablets, and portable gaming devices. In 2023, global shipments of premium smartphones grew by roughly 12 %, prompting manufacturers to adopt diffuser films that enhance brightness uniformity while reducing power consumption.

